INSERT INTO `aj_adv` VALUES ('29', '<p><a class=\"rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_link rich_media_meta_nickname\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU0NzI4ODU4OA==&mid=100000264&idx=1&sn=a01178049d405a04474822f615685859&chksm=7b51e16b4c26687d265bb0dc79da166d8c3805cd937eb5328824d70d6539ef7a98a7f9d1f174&mpshare=1&scene=1&srcid=03021ywL8FMVyzSkdsDPyPwD&key=a49ef7759e5f79b548f9c954155514c4eb4a8d573a3615d9036ea566edf4989cd5511a1c9fc52afc36a37e5e777f0d37da29e7c40d1ee31a2a9e291ca55fcf85ff36abf5f57dc04644772b6507854de4&ascene=1&uin=NzEzOTI3OTcy&devicetype=Windows+7&version=62060210&lang=zh_CN&pass_ticket=X6Mm5Yg%2FgW8LYXveq635xKjG81LxQ8fnLaFgnHge5ht3e89UC481QofghEukrEgW&winzoom=1##\" id=\"post-user\" style=\"white-space: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px 8px 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 149, 245); vertical-align: middle; max-width: none; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block !important;\">爱家房产网</a></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">全国人大透露未来五年立法规划 房地产税法等列入规划</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\">央视新闻：3月11日下午，十三届全国人大一次会议第三次全体会议在人民大会堂举行，听取全国人大常委会委员长张德江关于全国人民代表大会常务委员会工作的报告。全国人大透露未来五年立法规划，统筹安排今后五年立法工作。完善国家机构组织法，修改人民法院组织法、人民检察院组织法、公务员法等。完善建设现代化经济体系的法律制度，加快民法典编纂工作，审议民法典各分编；落实税收法定原则，制定耕地占用税法、车辆购置税法、资源税法等，研究制定房地产税法，修改税收征收管理法；制定外国投资法、电子商务法，修改农村土地承包法、土地管理法等。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.fang.xm0760.wang/data/upload/editor/image/201803/12/1520816360949799.jpg\" title=\"1520816360949799.jpg\" alt=\"1.JPG\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">何立峰:粤港澳大湾区发展规划纲要编制基本完成</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\">新华社：国家发展改革委主任何立峰9日在人民大会堂“部长通道”上说，目前粤港澳大湾区发展规划纲要的编制工作已基本完成，下一步将加快编制产业发展、交通、生态环境等方面的专项规划。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">地产融资成本飙升：贷款、发债普涨 信托成本增加</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\">21世纪：2018年以来，房地产融资成本大幅上升。有中部地产公司人士称，该公司短期融资利率12%左右，一年期融资利率9%左右，相比去年提高了3个百分点。从银行的贷款利率超过6%，比基准利率提价近三成。受到市场利率上升、表外金融监管等因素影响，房地产公司的资金成本上升较快，部分企业的融资渠道日渐狭窄。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.fang.xm0760.wang/data/upload/editor/image/201803/12/1520816370518986.jpg\" title=\"1520816370518986.jpg\" alt=\"2.JPG\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">南京多家银行首套房贷利率上浮15%-20%</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\">扬子晚报：南京目前有20家主流银行对首套房房贷政策利率上浮15%以上，还有不少银行上浮20%。对于二套房，上浮20%是主流，也有很多银行开始执行在基准利率基础上上浮25%或30%。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(191, 191, 191);\">【声明：以上内容来源房地产导刊，版权归原作者所有。我们对文中观点保持中立。如有侵权或不实，请及时联系小编删除。编辑：Mr.gao】</span></p><p>若内容有误或违规侵权，可立即：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://fang.xm0760.wang/home_wx/complaint.shtml?aid=47ed1631-2590-11e8-8b45-70106faffb64&laoshi=c13d5e46-1a9d-11e8-9816-7cd30ab8&rd=b037caa41ffb3904e648287b586c8228\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgb(66, 126, 186); background-color: transparent;\">举报/报错</a></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://aijfc.robot86.club/static/upload/image/20180310/1520670970942023988.gif\" class=\"img-responsive\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p></p><article tt-ignored-node=\"1\" style=\"wh