ng: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因为见多识广，他们审视一个城市的角度不一样，善于从国家政策层面，当地政策层面来把握一个城市的未来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMTQ5ODYzMA==&mid=2247491891&idx=1&sn=8f66cd499fe438620afe8e367e5141fc&chksm=e8397d5adf4ef44c2d23b2d5b1db920226e20bdab1916c9eb1eca6efd2bde2d3bf6b4cbe450c&scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 149, 245); text-decoration: none; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); text-decoration: underline; font-size: 17px;\">北海，为什么频上央视？因为“背景”很大，“后台”很硬！</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">北海海景房热销，还有一个重要原因，那就是从去年开始，政府出台生态立市的政策，已不再出让一线海景的住宅用地。这就意味着，海景资源的稀缺性日益凸显，并且越来越少。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在海边，拥有一间房子，面朝大海，冬暖花开，是多少内地人的梦想啊。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">北海的椰风海韵、</span>50<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">里长滩、温暖的冬天对他们产生极致的诱惑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMTQ5ODYzMA==&mid=2247491841&idx=1&sn=688d56488226b4ce82d3bb3dd35823aa&chksm=e8397d68df4ef47ecc5ad556fcf60e92ff70830e3756306248b8434dc668aa29cc1bd623f9ff&scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 149, 245); text-decoration: none; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/static/upload/image/20180315/1521124377039012973.jpg\" title=\"1521124377039012973.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20180315222642-04.jpg\"/></a></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMTQ5ODYzMA==&mid=2247491841&idx=1&sn=688d56488226b4ce82d3bb3dd35823aa&chksm=e8397d68df4ef47ecc5ad556fcf60e92ff70830e3756306248b8434dc668aa29cc1bd623f9ff&scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 149, 245); text-decoration: none; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/static/upload/image/20180315/1521124387055006851.jpg\" title=\"1521124387055006851.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20180315222652-05.jpg\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">前段时间有位作家写了篇文章，里面有一段说：上海人来了，他们象买白菜一样进售楼部就买，把北海的库存买光了。结果被售楼人员拿来在朋友圈儿狂转，北海楼市一时气氛骤紧、扑朔迷离。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其实，作家写文章是带有夸张手法的，虽然写的是前些年的事，但他并没有进行翔实的调研。本人长期跟踪观察北海楼市，从来没见过大批的上海人来北海买房；从去年开始，上海、淅江的确陆续来北海买房的人多了，但比起河北来买房的人数，那真没办法比。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">真正在北海拥有房产最多的外地人是前些年大量买烂尾楼的东北人和去年蜂涌而来的河北人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">北海楼市，未来谁主沉浮？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-c