pan style=\"font-family:微软雅黑 ;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">想要了解一个企业受大众的认可程度并不难，这是彰泰项目在桂林开盘的盛况，气势和一线房企的大型开盘盛况相比，不输分毫。</span></span><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p><img data-original=\"http://img.beihai365.com/bbs/photo/Mon_1710/208271_46dc150891920328db8fe9c9be4b8.jpg\" src=\"/static/upload/image/20171202/1512199570313089260.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" border=\"0\" style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑 ;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">彰泰目前在桂林的项目已经有30多个，包括住宅、别墅、公寓、酒店、大型商业体、特色客栈群等。在桂林市场独占鳌头！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑 ;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑 ;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">“桂林王“在广西的扩张之路</span></span></span></span><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑 ;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></span></span><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑 ;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">从深耕桂林到深耕广西，彰泰坚定扛起桂系地产领军大旗。</span></span><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑 ;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></span></span><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑 ;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">不仅仅局限于桂林，2017年彰泰已经在南宁、柳州、梧州、贺州、北海等广西核心城市进行了项目的布局，并挺进粤港澳大湾区。</span></span><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(5