 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2016年1—8月商品房销售面积87451万平方米，</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而2017年1—8月商品房销售面积98539万平方米，超出了10088万平方米。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">库存即将去化结束，新的楼市存量满足不了购房群体，房价不涨，更待何时？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三组数据，相信看官心里已有一本账，此时不出手买房，更待何时？</p><p class=\"pi\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/static/upload/image/20171204/1512359240572034080.jpg\" draggable=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（北海信息网）</p><p class=\"pi\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-hei