INSERT INTO `aj_news` VALUES ('28', '<article class=\"rich_media_content\" id=\"article\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 40px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); min-height: 350px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">有房贷数据显示，2017年全国首套房贷利率同比涨超20%。1月8日，央行官员发出重要“加息信号”。在房贷利率高涨的今天，如果央行再加息，楼市还看好吗？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.078125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" data-original=\"http://img.91zsxt.cn/upload/201801/8f554cf1-80a5-4af6-aa41-1f74b9dde855.png\" src=\"http://img.91zsxt.cn/upload/201801/8f554cf1-80a5-4af6-aa41-1f74b9dde855.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto !important; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 99, 95); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">要加息？！央行官员爆料了</span></span></span></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">在货币政策难言放松的背景下，央行是否会加息也引发市场关注。2017年12月的中央经济工作会议对2018年的货币政策给予明确定调。会议指出，稳健货币政策要保持中性，管住货币供给总闸门，保持货币信贷和社会融资规模合理增长。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">央行官员对于释放宽松信号也很谨慎。有媒体报道称中国人民银行研究局副局长纪敏表示“中国短期内仍存在加息空间”一事，纪敏1月8日随即表示，其近日在中国债券论坛上说，利率升降和杠杆率变化的关系，取决于投资回报率的动态变化。但这一理论表态，并不能解读为“短期内有加息空间”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">央行参事、原央行调查统计司司长盛松成1月6日在出席活动时表示，不主张甚至是反对目前中国加息，他指出，存贷款基准利率一上涨就等于为金融体、金融机构转嫁成本。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-backh=\"261\" data-backw=\"558\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/puibU2r1fAI2ia0lEtdKl1VsXwTsKmvXlC8Gy0AdvrHBaB4l2hRLiaT3SUEKSkwyRmOtptBSIelR8ibd7NyNZiaN9hg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-cropx1=\"0\" data-cropx2=\"1080\" data-cropy1=\"0\" data-cropy2=\"507.0967741935483\" data-ratio=\"0.4685185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"668px\" data-original=\"http://img.91zsxt.cn/upload/201801/7b347ac7-f96d-4c07-b467-960f3d9fb30d.png\" src=\"http://img.91zsxt.cn/upload/201801/7b347ac7-f96d-4c07-b467-960f3d9fb30d.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 668px !important; height: auto !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">▲</span>中国日报报道截图</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><section data-width=\"40px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.078125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" data-original=\"http://img.91zsxt.cn/upload/201801/1bb161bc-14c3-43c3-870a-49053be466a2.png\" src=\"http://img.91zsxt.cn/upload/201801/1bb161bc-14c3-43c3-870a-49053be466a2.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto !important; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/></p></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 99, 95); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">加息还没开始，房贷利率可涨上去了</span></span></span></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">不过，也有机构观点认为，央行在2018年将会采取加息举措。对于我们普通老百姓来说，加息就意味着房贷又涨了。目前，加息还没来，但全国房贷利率2017年已涨超20%，并仍在继续上涨。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">1月9日，根据某房地产监测数据显示，2017年12月全国首套房贷款平均利率为5.38%，相当于基准利率1.098倍，同比2016年12月首套房贷款平均利率4.45%，上升20.89%，相当于2017年12月贷款100万元买房，要比一年前多还20余万元。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">同时，业内人士普遍认为，房贷利率还有上升可能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">某研究院智库中心研究总监严跃进表示，<span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2018年整个资金方面的成本将会有所提升，对相应的购房需求，尤其是非刚需、非首套的购房需求会有所遏制，从信贷方面来看，房贷利率的提升将是一个大概率事件。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">著名分析师李唯一认为，就目前来看，资金层面亦未表现出宽松的趋势，货币政策仍为稳健型，长效机制未完全发力。2018年房贷利率变化趋势出现“急刹车”和“猛加油”现象的可能性小，将会继续保持目前状态呈小幅低速上涨。同时，未来或会有更多二线城市再度执行房贷利率上调。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">一线城市部分银行相关人员表示，暂未收到明确执行上调15%的通知，但不排除统一上调的可能性。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; wo