00%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">如果你有首付、有购房资格，而且是刚需，抓紧时间买房子，因为一旦加息，购房成本和还贷成本都会更高。事实证明，目前的购房成本已经够高了，所以在不抓紧上车，以后只能越来越难。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">去杠杆，很多人靠高杠杆获得很多利润，但是从去年开始，很多会议都强调要去杠杆，所以不管是个人还是企业还是要紧跟政策。另外，央行一旦加息，加杠杆的成本会不断攀升，可能会给自己增加压力！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">对</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">于央行是否加息、房贷利率一涨再涨，未来买房成本有多高，这些都是我们不能决定的，我们能决定的就是，提高警惕，合理配置手里的资源，需要买房的时候就抓紧上车！</span></span></span></p></article><p><br/></p>', '2018-02-28 11:02:37.160000', '1', '1', '重磅！各地首套房贷利率再上调！买房的该下手了！', '2', '1', '314', '/static/upload/image/20180117/1516169792956046377.jpg', '爱家房产网');
