ding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">北海得天独厚的滨海风光和气候环境还吸引了许多人来此置业、生活，尤其是作为全国最受欢迎的冬季候鸟迁徙目的地之一，每逢冬季北海的海景度假房源必遭哄抢。相对于大连、青岛、厦门，北海气候温暖湿润，冬暖夏凉，是闻名遐迩的度假休闲胜地。不想在北方大雪纷飞瑟瑟发抖，那就在北海的碧海蓝天温暖过冬吧！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/d6aSlBwDHKfh5RWLEcLN1ZVWPZ16OjPibicMy8CoLToFpyQe6icoeh1ftBgdJPyjVGqrjzUbyCuOAoRibdSPteyRjw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-copyright=\"0\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-w=\"1182\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/d6aSlBwDHKfh5RWLEcLN1ZVWPZ16OjPibicMy8CoLToFpyQe6icoeh1ftBgdJPyjVGqrjzUbyCuOAoRibdSPteyRjw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/d6aSlBwDHKcYzcVWtvmSDYb9dRA6m6icGXKIUR4IQ95nxchmVjlEaibHhzxCW1C7wGjicde3cVgLBwFWRs9VpwGbA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-copyright=\"0\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5345454545454545\" data-w=\"550\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/d6aSlBwDHKcYzcVWtvmSDYb9dRA6m6icGXKIUR4IQ95nxchmVjlEaibHhzxCW1C7wGjicde3cVgLBwFWRs9VpwGbA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"marg