场、高铁站及核心商圈、景区的路线皆很方便，出入均无障碍；再次，项目此次开盘产品为高赠送比的9层电梯洋房，在所有的后期规划中都不会再有，因此其稀缺性异常明显”，所以，有如此高的关注度也属正常了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img border=\"0\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6672727272727272\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/g8lMlhq9iaxBFd9wTR3BnKicU0OycNiaRF1fb5MicKyvo6RRicahZpGNTjR2SA5VicH0QrrrXI4H5dohCeCNDS8ChUkw/\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"550\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/g8lMlhq9iaxBFd9wTR3BnKicU0OycNiaRF1fb5MicKyvo6RRicahZpGNTjR2SA5VicH0QrrrXI4H5dohCeCNDS8ChUkw/?tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none; border: 0px; display: inline; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/><img border=\"0\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/g8lMlhq9iaxBFd9wTR3BnKicU0OycNiaRF1cHEALQH4Okv953w50D9QP1eiaibBSYpDHdC8lJ7LSfpVZCea2FLYUCRw/\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1200\" width=\"548\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/g8lMlhq9iaxBFd9wTR3BnKicU0OycNiaRF1cHEALQH4Okv953w50D9QP1eiaibBSYpDHdC8lJ7LSfpVZCea2FLYUCRw/?tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; outline: none; border: 0px; display: inline; height: 452px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 548px; visibility: visible !important;\" height=\"452\"/><img border=\"0\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6672727272727272\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/g8lMlhq9iaxBFd9wTR3BnKicU0OycNiaRF1ibmCTpdtWricSumTFCleXic6O0kzJB7pT1EqicyPNR4KdnYW4LM0ibeydaA/\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"550\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/g8lMlhq9iaxBFd9wTR3BnKicU0OycNiaRF1ibmCTpdtWricSumTFCleXic6O0kzJB7pT1EqicyPNR4KdnYW4LM0ibeydaA/?tp=webp&wx