eak-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; 截至本文发稿时，中电·海湾国际社区项目开盘当日总销售量超300套，总销额破亿元！在北海市房地产市场以及廉州湾片区2018年首季度商业版图内画出了一个红彤彤的对勾！中电·海湾国际社区的开盘建设，必将为北海市北部湾腾飞梦想添翼，同时也标志着北海市廉州湾片区建设翻开了一个新的篇章。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2018-02-28 10:45:27.082000', '1', '1', '“北海北花开连连，廉州湾腾飞在即” ——中电·海湾国际社区华丽登场', '1', '2', '64', '/static/upload/image/20180123/1516673468867004694.jpg', '爱家房产网');
INSERT INTO `aj_news` VALUES ('41', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 17px;\">看到身边的人一个个买了房子，很多人都会矛盾：一方面觉得别人都有房了，自己没有，抬不起头；但另一方面又会怀疑，为了一套房子，肩负30年的房贷，内心不会感到恐慌吗？这样究竟值不值得？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.57\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/fYrbv3AClpkCpDuh1iaQu9XbaWt8tkrzia17f6lPrtibsqr2Eib91M8JvmpN5