 !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 17px\">一片空地，那叫投资；配套都有了，那叫追涨；社区成熟了，那叫结盘。<br style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"/>在中国的一二线城市买个80平米的房子，光好的地段首付可能就要大几十万，更别说地段好、房型好、配套全的。如果你非要什么都好的，要求可以理解，但价钱你也要理解！<span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">记住，没有十全十美的房子。房子，好才贵。</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 2em;letter-spacing: 2px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 2em;letter-spacing: 2px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 17px\">对于一个普通家庭很难一下在掏出那么多钱。所以，在在这种情况下，可以考虑地理位置稍微偏点的地方。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 2em;letter-spacing: 2px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 17px\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box 