dent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">北海楼市犹如火箭一般，直冲天际，用疯狂、高热来形容并不为过。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">据网上房地产相关数据显示，2017年1-12月北海楼市新房销售量39713套，同比2016年的23689套上涨了67.64%，成为北海楼市新房销售量史上最高的一年，平均到每个月的销售量为3309套。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><img src=\"/static/upload/image/20180128/1517148644651057344.jpg\" title=\"1517148644651057344.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20180128220906.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"/></p><section class=\"\" label=\"Powered by bj.96weixin.com\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section class=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section data-by=\"96weixin\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: center\"><section style=\";padding: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;display: inline-block;background: rgb(216, 40, 33)\"><section style=\";padding: 2px 5px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 1px dotted rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><section style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 24px\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">供不应求 库存告急</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">2017年北海市新房销售总量已接近4万套，从开年就处于一种供不应求的状态，摇号抢房、日空盘、时光盘，甚至买豪宅也如砍瓜切菜……</p><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">尤其在上半年，以北方人为主的外溢投资客蜂拥而至，一下就将北海多年积累的存量瓜分得七七八八。最直观的表现就是<span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;text-indent: 2em\">北海大多数楼盘都经历了逢开售罄或热销的火爆，动不动就线上开盘秒罄刷屏</span>的疯狂节奏<span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;text-indent: 2em\">。现金为王、全款优先、贷款稍等、热门楼盘一房难求……更是出现阶段性房荒现象。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><img src=\"/static/upload/image/20180128/1517148745761068867.jpg\" title=\"1517148745761068867.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20180128220941.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"/></p><section class=\"\" label=\"Powered by bj.96weixin.com\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section class=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section data-by=\"96weixin\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: center\"><section style=\";padding: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;display: inline-block;background: rgb(216, 40, 33)\"><section style=\";padding: 2px 5px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 1px dotted rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><section style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 24px\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">最强楼市调控政策接踵而来</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">2017年北海楼市的疯狂结束在第三季度。限购、限售、严控备案价……北海宣布加入全国“N限”豪华大餐。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">调控新政连番轰炸后，北海楼市确实没那么疯狂了，但“高房价、稳成交”已成楼市常态。加之开发商“丰富”的销售经验，哪怕不绑车位、不做装修，来个霸气的一价清，也能赚得盆满钵满，不过就是赚多赚少罢了，已经稳赢。<img data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/K0lVia0picJr1X9LtWBChfppHcbtsK9RUicJR9hgL0lprZKr1375z5Y6Aqq2j97mV8e17fxOaXsKj8RnRXNv66YaQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4625\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/K0lVia0picJr1X9LtWBChfppHcbtsK9RUicJR9hgL0lprZKr1375z5Y6Aqq2j97mV8e17fxOaXsKj8RnRXNv66YaQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\";padding: 0px;height: auto !important;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;text-indent: 2em;width: auto !important;visibility: visible !important\"/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><img data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/K0lVia0picJr1X9LtWBChfppHcbtsK9RUic00LRtcN8ibcORetfJacUg7CSUNsnBojpia7XOMQ47DztDbU8MPpQxhHQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.29375\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/K0lVia0picJr1X9LtWBChfppHcbtsK9RUic00LRtcN8ibcORetfJacUg7CSUNsnBojpia7XOMQ47DztDbU8MPpQxhHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\";padding: 0px;height: auto !important;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: auto !important;visibility: visible !important\"/></p><section class=\"\" label=\"Powered by bj.96weixin.com\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section class=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section data-by=\"96weixin\" style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><section style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: center\"><section style=\";padding: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;display: inline-block;background: rgb(216, 40, 33)\"><section style=\";padding: 2px 5px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 1px dotted rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><section style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 24px\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">2018年：<span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-indent: 32px\">品质年</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">随着疯狂褪去，有些楼盘由于地段、产品、配套等局限而开始沉寂。反之，那些地段好、品牌佳、配套足的楼盘就越来越热了。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">2018年将是一个品质年。一方面，改善<span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">客群</span>已成置业主流，他们希望住更好、更舒适的房子。另一方面，十九大报告指出,现阶段我国社会主要矛盾已经转化为“人民日益增长的美好生活需要和不平衡不充分的发展之间的矛盾”。对于楼市同样适用——房子并不是<span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">数量</span>不够，而是质量不够好、分布不够平衡。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\">所以，除了行情所致，归根究底还是楼盘品质的竞争，</span>而不是一拥而上。这样的购房方式才是居住本来的样子。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"/></p></section></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(255, 41, 65)\">【转载声明】<span style=\"padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">本文数据材料</span></span></strong>转载于北海房地产交易网站</p><p><br/></p>', '2018-02-28 10:50:15.800000', '1', '1', '史上最高！2017年北海新房成交量破纪录', '1', '2', '328', '/static/upload/image/20180128/1517148916979008171.jpg', '爱家房产网');
