9;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">早在2016年，银监会就下发了闻风丧胆的55号文——</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">不得将信托资金违规投向房地产、地方政府融资平台、股票市场、产能过剩等限制或禁止领域。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">也就是说，早在2016年信托的口子就被堵上了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">2018年，信托去杠杆仍将持续发力。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">以前很多开发商通过信托撬动杠杆大概是按照1:2的比例，比如说，开发商有1亿的自有资金，就可以搞出来2个亿的钱，之后拿着3个亿的资金杀入土地市场中。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">未来可能需要开发商把多吃进去的1个亿强制性的退出来</span>，<span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">把杠杆强制性的降低到1:1以下。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; m