style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(23, 110, 186);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二，避开一切跟房地产有关的信贷、基金、信托、P2P等等。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">对于诸多中小房企开发商来说，未来的两年一定是越来越难熬的两年，正规渠道的钱越来越难搞到，债务累计越来越多。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">在这样的大背景下，肯定有部分开发商跳到民间借贷、违规投资担保之中去，给出的利息还一定不会低，在这个时候就是考验“<span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">智商和欲望</span>”的时候了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">还是那句话，这年头握着硬邦邦的钱，比啥都强。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(23, 110, 186);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第三，房价或许会下调，与此同时机会也会伴随到来。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; wor