: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(23, 110, 186);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第四，最好别碰地王、别碰CEO盘。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">尤其是那些地方型中小房企开发的那些地王项目，在吃紧的资金压力下，面对如此重的财务成本压力，要么他们会辗转死去，要么会甩开节操，牺牲品质，低价倾销。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em !important; background-c