ily: 宋体;\">1# </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">均价</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">12000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">元</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平米 有 </span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">多套房源 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">31</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日交房</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">5# <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">均价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平米 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2019.12.31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交房 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">85</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折六套以上佣金</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">450</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元每平米，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折六套以下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">350</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元 </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6#</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">号楼期房认购，认筹金</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">万，</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2017.12-2018</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年元旦开盘 全款有优先选房权</span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '2017-12-16 01:26:32.237000', '2', '1', '爱家房产网：北海楼盘佣金明细表');
