INSERT INTO `aj_premise` VALUES ('2', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">2018-02-06&nbsp;22:55:06</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 33px; widows: 1; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【恒大海上帝景】</span></strong><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 33px; widows: 1; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">是继恒大御景半岛、恒大名都后，恒大集团在北海落地的第三个项目。项目南与北部湾为伴，东邻银滩，西接国际标准十八杆高尔夫、国家4A景点冠头岭森林公园，北连主干道新世纪大道，尊享24公里一线银滩，海景景观优美，环境秀丽，是北海银滩西区上的一线亲海美宅。&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 33px; widows: 1; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 33px; widows: 1; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【恒大海上帝景】</span></strong><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 33px; widows: 1; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">项目总占地302.39亩，分为南北两个地块，其中北地块以洋房和高层为主，建筑面积约291197㎡，容积率2.5，绿化率30%。南地块以公寓为主，建筑面积约127673㎡，容积率1.5，绿化率30%。&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 33px; widows: 1; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 33px; widows: 1; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-