class=\"con_y\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></span></strong></p><p class=\"con_y\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">【户型说明】</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">推出四房两厅两卫产品125m²、140m²；五房两厅两卫260m²，碧桂园北海印象所处的铁路南片区，承接着老城区政治、文化、商业转移及功能升级，位于城市发展轴上，亦是这座城市的潜力所向。以国际豪宅社区理念，规划有10幢高层洋房、商业街、会所、露天泳池、儿童乐园、康体设施等。高尔夫七重景观园林，享誉全国。</span></span></p><p class=\"con_y\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></span><br/></p>', '2018-02-20 11:36:55.818000', '1', '1', '碧桂园北海印象', '北海市银海区广东路万达广场附近', '42.79', '9800.00', '71000', '碧桂园集团', '10', '新房2018-006', '2.5', '30%', '5581', '【现推出2#127㎡洋房新品同样是纯南向一字板式楼，南北通透】【2019年豪装交房】【产权70年】', null, '/static/upload/image/20180220/1519097803146024976_wt.jpg|/static/upload/image/20171124/1511492100212042464_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt.jpg|/static/upload/image/20171124/1511492108165097131_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt.jpg|/static/upload/image/20171124/1511492112462081894_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_wt_